SQL_STMT_U.val: select MASAV_RETURN_CODE,COUNT(*) total_for_return_code , (select count(1) from A_TASHLUMIM t where t.DATE_ERECH between ':1' and ':2' and STATUS_TASHLUM=6 and SUG_TASHLUM=0) total from A_TASHLUMIM t inner join A_MEYDA_NOSAF mn on mn.NUMERATOR=t.NUMERATOR_TIK and t.LINE_NO=mn.LINE_NO where t.DATE_ERECH between ':1' and ':2' and STATUS_TASHLUM=6 and SUG_TASHLUM=0 group by MASAV_RETURN_CODE order by total_for_return_code desc
